(1009, NULL, 'Delaware', 'Summer Math Modeling Program for rising juniors and seniors', '11-12', 'Prerequisites are Algebra I and Geometry.', NULL, '2025-05-19', 'https://www.udel.edu/academics/colleges/cas/units/departments/mathematical-sciences/about-us/summer-programs/summer-math-modeling-high-school/?utm_source=chatgpt.com', 'Academic Program', 'Math', 'Outside School', '5‑day nonresidential program (free) for rising juniors & seniors in high school who are interested in mathematical modeling, working on real problems with UD faculty/grad students. Earn a stipend.Participants get a stipend of $600 upon completion.', '2025-11-13 21:31:08', '2025-11-24 22:36:33'),
